      "description": "PROD-DEPLOY GATE: cycle-23 завершает security+monitoring layer (rate-limit persist,\nCSP/HSTS, /api/health). cycle-24 закрывает functional regression layer через e2e.\n\nTools: @playwright/test + vitest (browser-context mode).\n\nCritical user paths to cover (15 scenarios minimum):\n  1. login page renders 200 + form fields visible + no console errors\n  2. login submit wrong credentials → show error banner (no 500)\n  3. login submit good credentials → redirect /dashboard + nav shows username\n  4. /dashboard loads with KPI tiles + activity stream\n  5. /proposals list renders rows + filter input works\n  6. /proposals/new — добавление товара из списка -> cart updates -> save → 201\n  7. /contracts list + status badge colors match STATUS_MAP\n  8. /production/gantt loads columns + tasks visible + status colors match\n  9. /production/gantt drag-resize task → PUT 200, payload sent to /api/order-tasks/:id\n 10. /warehouse page — storage items list + click row → detail panel\n 11. /finance/order-closings — create new closing with status=draft → row appears\n 12. /admin/users — create user (admin only) + role=editor; sign-out + log in as new user\n 13. /api/health returns 200 + JSON shape { status, db, uptime, version, timestamp }\n 14. /api/health 503 path: switch DATABASE_URL invalid → expect 503\n 15. CSP enforcement: inline script without nonce → browser blocks → console.error\n\nFile layout:\n  tests/e2e/ — *.spec.ts (Playwright)\n  vitest.config.ts — add projects: [{ extends: ..., test.include: \"tests/e2e/**/*.spec.ts\" }]\n  playwright.config.ts — baseURL=http://localhost:3000, headless:true, webServer: npm run dev\n\nHelpers to install:\n  pnpm add -D @playwright/test  (or npm install -D @playwright/test)\n  pnpm exec playwright install --with-deps chromium\n\nCI integration:\n  .github/workflows/e2e.yml (or gitlab-ci.yml / Jenkinsfile) — run Playwright on PR/push to main.\n  Run AFTER tsc+lint+vitest unit (gate). Upload Playwright report + screenshots on failure.\n\nAcceptance:\n  All 15 scenarios PASS\n  0 console errors / page errors on any happy path\n  Total runtime under 5 minutes (test execution parallelized via Playwright workers: 4)\n  vitest 64/64 + e2e 15/15 both green in CI\n  Fail-fast on any 500/console-error (test counts as FAIL even if assertion passed)\n\nOut-of-scope (deferred):\n  Load testing (k6 / artillery) — separate cycle after deploy to staging\n  Visual regression (chromatic / percy) — nice-to-have but not blocking deploy\n  a11y automated checks (axe-core) — already covered manually; auto check could be cycle-25\n\nFiles to create:\n  tests/e2e/ (15 .spec.ts files, one per scenario)\n  playwright.config.ts\n  tests/e2e/helpers/ (loginAs, waitForRoute, expectNoConsoleErrors shared helpers)\n  .github/workflows/e2e.yml\n\nAfter: node agent-cli.js mimo done cycle-24-p2-e2e-playwright",
